data.description: Immaculate and Move-in ready built in 2019. Three bedrooms, two bathrooms. Open concept/split floor plan. Large living room will accommodate plenty of seating. Kitchen has Stainless-steel appliances, upgraded gorgeous white cabinetry w/ SS hardware, Granite countertops with coordinating subway tiled backsplash. Pendant lighting over the full-utility island/bar with 60/40 SS sink. Trendy designer wall pantry allows for additional concentrated storage within the kitchen - without losing valuable floor space. Drop zone in laundry room! Located in the desirable Battle Creek - Broken Arrow School district. Great location: Easy highway access, nearby shopping centers, dining options, and cozy cafe's.
